I will utilize different levels of functionality while developing this application in order to maximize usefulness. 

Stages of developement will include:
	1. Pogostick
		-Accounts UI and registration capabilities
		-Rough styling choices (font, color pallet)
		-Zip code entry form and record zip in user data
		-Automated email capability
	2. Scateboard
		-Give thought to wireframes and navigation via email
		-Homepage with goodies, such as a twitter feed and current weather, tips from blog/ news stream
		-Dates for first frost and last frost
	3. Bicycle
		-Ability to select crops and recieve start dates for germination
		-App store availiablity? 
		-Responsive layout
	4. Glider
		-Garden layout planning? Containers? Auto-arrange plants

